### ============================================================
### 会话管理接口
### ============================================================

### 变量定义
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken =

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 获取所有活跃会话列表
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 删除指定会话 (替换 {sessionId} 为实际 ID)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/sessions/{{sessionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
